<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-10 16:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6487 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STOLENCHILDREN-1200(2     08-10 0712
