$2 million for the conviction of the terrorists who attacked two
embassies. State Department draws up multimillion-dollar plans for
increasing security at hundreds of buildings overseas. By David L.
Marcus. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
