work to nonunion subsidiaries are major issues in talks between
Bell Atlantic and 73,000 striking workers. &UR;  &LR; By Diane E. Lewis. 900
words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   BELL-IMPACT (Undated) -- Bell Atlantic customers waiting for 411
service, installations, and other services can expect some delays.
But the impact is muted because so many services are automated. By
Ronald Rosenberg. 500 words.
</P>
<P>
   OCEAN-PEPSI (Undated) -- Ocean Spray Cranberries seeks an
injunction to block PepsiCo from using its distribution channels to
deliver Tropicana juices to convenience stores. By Chris Reidy. 600
words.
</P>
