<P>
   BC-COLO-JONBENET-NYT (moved on Friday, August 7)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Friday, August 7,
about calls for a special prosecutor in the JonBenet Ramsey case in
Boulder, Colo., misidentified the party affiliation of Craig
Silverman, a Denver trial lawyer. He is registered as an
independent, not as a Republican.
</P>
