   &QL; 
GLF-CARTS (Los Angeles) _ Feature on golf carts, or Casey Martin
played here. The case for carts for the rest of us. Do they make
the game faster, slower, better? View of area course managers and
golfers and history and growth of this trend, which has definitely
changed the game, for better or worse, depending on your
viewpoint. &QL; 
By Jarre Fees. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
