<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-VINEYARD-BOX-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Facts about martha's vineyard
 &HT;    (EDS: With VINEYARD and VINEYARD-SCANDAL. DUPLICATION ALERT:
Moving in (l) Lifestyle and (w) Washington categories.)
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   POPULATION:
</P>
<P>
   Winter................14,773
</P>
<P>
   Summer...........102,193
</P>
<P>
   AVERAGE TEMPERATURE.........HIGH.....LOW
</P>
<P>
   July.................................................78............6
2
</P>
<P>
   August...........................................78............62
</P>
<P>
   December.....................................43............27
</P>
<P>
   January.........................................37............21
</P>
<P>
   Geography:
</P>
<P>
   Location: 7 miles off Cape Cod, Mass.
</P>
<P>
   Area: about 100 square miles
</P>
<P>
   Length: 23 miles at longest point
</P>
<P>
   Width: 9 miles at widest point
</P>
<P>
   Waterfront: 124.6 miles of tidal shoreline, plus several
interior ponds.
</P>
