<SLUG> BC-REFUGEES-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Group from Haiti smuggled to U.S. waters, left on sandbar; one
dead
 &HT;    (EDS: Runs with ASHORE-COX and REFUGEE-RELATIVES-COX. Stories
will move on (a) National and (i) International wires.)
 &HT;    By Tim Pallesen
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
