<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-BBO-BEANIE-BABIES-NYT, which
moved in ``s'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I expected kids to clamor for it, but it was fun to watch
grown men with their Beanie Babies. And you'd be surprised how many
players have their own collections.''
</P>
<P>
   _MARK GORRIS, major league baseball official.
</P>
